707969f-a.title: Manhattan: 2nd Avenue - 122nd Street (East)
707969f-a.text:
Second Ave., north from but not including East 122nd Street, showing the
center roadway after street car track removal by the W.P.A. Note the
station of the Second Ave. Elevated Line at East 125th Street.
October 28, 1936.
W.P.A. Photo.
Federal Art Project.
CREDIT LINE IMPERATIVE ON ALL REPRODUCTIONS.
